#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:265
msgid "Display & Style"
msgstr "Affichage & Style"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:267
msgid ""
"These settings describe the way the order form is displayed to your "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"Ces paramètres décrivent la façon dont le formulaire de commande est affiché "
"à vos clients."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:272
msgid "Order Form Style"
msgstr "Style du formulaire de commande"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:277
msgid ""
"Standard (Add to cart per row) - shows an add to cart button per row which "
"is faster for customers."
msgstr ""
"Standard (Ajout au panier par ligne)  - affiche un bouton Ajouter au panier "
"par ligne ce qui est plus rapide pour les clients."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:278
msgid ""
"Alternate (Add to cart at bottom) - select boxes per row with an add to cart "
"button at the bottom of the form."
msgstr ""
"Alternatif (Ajouter au panier en bas) - des coches de sélection par ligne et "
"un bouton Ajouter au panier au bas du formulaire."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:283
msgid "Order Form Paging Style"
msgstr "Style de page du formulaire de commande"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:288
msgid "Paginated - split results into pages based on the products per page."
msgstr ""
"Paginé - divise les résultats en pages selon ne nombre de produits par page."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:289
msgid ""
"Lazy Loading - more results are loaded into the page based on the user "
"scrolling."
msgstr ""
"Chargement paresseux - plus de produits sont chargés dans la page à mesure "
"que l’utilisateur la fait défiler."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:294
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-i18n-controller.php:398
msgid "Products Per Page"
msgstr "Produits par page"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:296
msgid ""
"The number of products loaded per page if paginated or the number of "
"products fetched at a time during scrolling when lazy loading."
msgstr ""
"Le nombre de produits chargés par page si paginé ou le nombre de produits "
"récupérés à chaque fois pendant le défilement en cas de chargement paresseux."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:303
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-settings-controller.php:184
msgid "Show Variations Individually"
msgstr "Montrer les variations de produits individuellement"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:305
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-settings-controller.php:186
msgid ""
"Enabling this setting will list down each product variation individually and "
"have its own row in the wholesale order form."
msgstr ""
"Activer ce paramètre listera chaque variation de produit individuellement "
"ainsi chacune aura sa propre ligne dans le formulaire de commande en gros."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:310
msgid "Product Click Action"
msgstr "Action du clic sur le produit"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:315
msgid ""
"Navigate To Single Product Page - takes the user to the single product page "
"for that product."
msgstr ""
"Naviguer vers la page produit - amène l’utilisateur sur la page produit "
"simple de ce produit."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:316
msgid ""
"Show A Product Details Popup - shows the user a popup without leaving the "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Afficher les détails produit dans une fenêtre - montre à l’utilisateur une "
"fenêtre surgissante sans quitter la page."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:321
msgid "Display Extra Columns"
msgstr "Afficher des colonnes en plus"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:323
#: templates/wwof-product-listing-alternate-lazyload.php:19
#: templates/wwof-product-listing-alternate.php:22
msgid "Stock Quantity"
msgstr "Quantité en stock"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:331
msgid "Product SKU"
msgstr "UGS du produit"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:339
msgid "Product Thumbnail"
msgstr "Vignette du produit"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:345
msgid "Product Thumbnail Size"
msgstr "Taille de vignette du produit"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:358
msgid "Show Cart Subtotal"
msgstr "Afficher le sous-total du panier"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:360
msgid "Shows the current cart subtotal at the bottom of the form."
msgstr "Affiche le sous-total courant du panier en bas du formulaire."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:365
msgid "Hide Wholesale Quantity Based Pricing Tables"
msgstr "Cacher les tables de prix de gros en fonction de la quantité"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:367
msgid ""
"If a product has additional quantity based pricing a table is normally shown "
"which can take a lot of vertical space. When checked, this will hide that "
"table."
msgstr ""
"Si un produit bénéficie de prix de gros en fonction de la quantité une table "
"est normalement affichée ce qui prend beaucoup d’espace verticalement. Quand "
"l’option est cochée, la table est cachée."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:372
msgid "Show Wholesale Order Requirements"
msgstr "Afficher les conditions de commande en gros"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:374
msgid ""
"If minimum order requirements are defined in WooCommerce Wholesale Prices "
"Premium, show a notice at the top of the form to let customers know what "
"they have to do."
msgstr ""
"Si des conditions minimales de commande sont définies dans WooCommerce "
"Wholesale Prices Premium, affiche une notification en tête du formulaire "
"pour informer les clients de ce qu’ils ont à faire."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:378
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-i18n-controller.php:227
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-i18n-controller.php:235
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Oui"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:379
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-i18n-controller.php:228
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-i18n-controller.php:236
msgid "No"
msgstr "Non"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:390
msgid "Search & Filtering"
msgstr "Recherche & Filtrage"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:392
msgid ""
"These settings related to the searchability and filterability of the order "
"form as well as the sorting."
msgstr ""
"Les paramètres liés à la recherche et au filtrage du formulaire de commande "
"mais également au tri."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:397
msgid "Allow Zero Inventory Products"
msgstr "Permettre les produits sans inventaire"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:399
msgid "Let products with no inventory be shown in the form."
msgstr ""
"Permet aux produits sans inventaire d’être affichés dans le formulaire."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:404
msgid "Allow Search By SKU"
msgstr "Permettre la recherche par UGS"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:406
msgid "Let customers search for products by their product SKU."
msgstr "Permet aux clients de rechercher les produits par leur numéro UGS."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:411
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-settings-controller.php:150
msgid "Product Sorting"
msgstr "Tri des produits"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:413
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-settings-controller.php:152
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-settings-controller.php:167
msgid "Changes how products are sorted on the form."
msgstr "Change la façon dont les produits sont triés dans le formulaire."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:420
msgid "Product Sort Order"
msgstr "Ordre de tri des produits"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:426
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-i18n-controller.php:658
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-settings-controller.php:171
msgid "Ascending"
msgstr "Croissant"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:427
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-i18n-controller.php:659
#: includes/v2/api/controllers/class-rest-api-settings-controller.php:172
msgid "Descending"
msgstr "Décroissant"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:437
msgid "Misc"
msgstr "Divers"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:439
msgid ""
"These settings handle other miscellaneous parts of the way your order form "
"works."
msgstr ""
"Ces paramètres gèrent divers autres aspects du fonctionnement de votre "
"formulaire."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:444
msgid "Cart Subtotal Tax"
msgstr "Sous-total des taxes du panier"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:446
msgid ""
"Choose if the cart subtotal should display including or excluding taxes. "
"This is only used if you have the <i>Show Cart Subtotal</i> setting turned "
"on."
msgstr ""
"Choisissez si le sous-total panier doit inclure les taxes ou non. Ceci est "
"uniquement utilisé si vous avez activé <i>Afficher le sous-total du panier</"
"i>."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:450
msgid "Including tax"
msgstr "Taxes inclues"

# x
#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:451
msgid "Excluding tax"
msgstr "Hors taxes"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:491
msgid "No Default"
msgstr "Aucune valeur par défaut"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:496
msgid "Product Filtering"
msgstr "Filtrage produit"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:498
msgid ""
"The filtering options below control which products are shown or not shown on "
"the order form."
msgstr ""
"Les options de filtrage ci-dessous contrôlent quels produits sont affichés "
"ou non dans le formulaire de commande."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:503
msgid "Filter Product Categories"
msgstr "Filtrer les catégories produit"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:505
msgid ""
"Tell the order form which categories it should draw products from and don't "
"show products from any other categories. Leave this empty to show products "
"from all categories."
msgstr ""
"Dit au formulaire de commande de quelles catégories il devrait afficher les "
"produits et masquer ceux de toutes autres catégories. Laisser vide pour "
"afficher les produits de toutes les catégories."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:511
msgid "Select Some Product Categories..."
msgstr "Sélectionnez des catégories de produits…"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:517
msgid "Default Category Filter"
msgstr "Filtre de catégorie par défaut"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:519
msgid ""
"Pre-filter the order form on load by specifying a default category on the "
"search box."
msgstr ""
"Pré-filtre le formulaire de commande au chargement en spécifiant une "
"catégorie par défaut dans la boîte de recherche."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:527
msgid "Exclude Products"
msgstr "Exclure des produits"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:529
msgid "Specify specific products to hide from the order form product list."
msgstr ""
"Définit des produits spécifiques à masquer dans la liste de produits du "
"formulaire de commande."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:534
msgid "Select Some Products..."
msgstr "Sélectionnez des produits…"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:569
msgid "Permissions Options"
msgstr "Options de permissions"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:576
msgid "User Role Filter"
msgstr "Filtre de rôles utilisateurs"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:578
msgid ""
"Only allow a given user role/s to access the wholesale page. Left blank to "
"disable filter."
msgstr ""
"Autorise uniquement le(s) rôle(s) défini(s) à accéder à la page grossiste. "
"Laisser vide pour désactiver ce filtre."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:585
msgid "Select Some User Roles..."
msgstr "Sélectionnez des rôles utilisateurs…"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:596
msgid "Access Denied Message"
msgstr "Message d’accès refusé"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:598
msgid ""
"Message to display to users who do not have permission to access the "
"wholesale order form."
msgstr ""
"Message à afficher aux utilisateurs qui n’ont pas la permission d’accéder au "
"formulaire de commande en gros."

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:603
msgid "Title"
msgstr "Titre"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:605
msgid "Defaults to <b>\"Access Denied\"</b> if left blank"
msgstr "Par défaut <b>\"Accès refusé\"</b> si laissé vide"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:612
msgid "Message"
msgstr "Message"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:614
msgid ""
"Defaults to <b>\"You do not have permission to view wholesale product listing"
"\"</b> if left blank"
msgstr ""
"Par défaut <b>\"Vous n’avez pas la permission de voir la liste des produits "
"grossistes\"</b> si laissé vide"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:621
msgid "Login URL"
msgstr "URL de connexion"

#: includes/class-wwof-settings.php:623
